---
import CvLayout from '../layouts/CvLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<CvLayout
  seo={{
    title: 'Clinton Foundation',
    description: 'Clinton Global Initiative University at UC Berkeley. Developed a business model to provide sustainable education solutions in the slums.'
  }}
  breadcrumb="Clinton Foundation"
>
  <div class="cv-box cv-box--subpage">
    <div class="cv-subpage-header">
      <div class="cv-subpage-category"><Icon name="ph:tag" class="cv-subpage-category__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Humanitarian project</div>
      <h1 class="cv-subpage-title">Clinton Foundation</h1>
      <div class="cv-subpage-meta">
        <p><Icon name="ph:map-pin" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> University of Berkeley, United States</p>
        <p><Icon name="ph:calendar" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> April 1-3, 2016</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-content">
      <p>The Clinton Global Initiative University represents a community of emerging leaders tackling global challenges through concrete action. Thomas Rouaud created an economic framework designed to deliver enduring solutions adapted for education initiatives in underserved communities. His work earned him selection into this prestigious program, where he met Bill Clinton during the April 2016 UC Berkeley event.</p>

      <div class="cv-subpage-images">
        <img src="/images/clinton-foundation-1.jpg" alt="Thomas Rouaud at Clinton Foundation" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/clinton-foundation-2.jpg" alt="UNIL delegation in San Francisco" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-footer">
      <a href="/" class="cv-subpage-back"><Icon name="ph:arrow-left" class="cv-subpage-back__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Retour à la page d'accueil</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</CvLayout>
